#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Avijjāvagga"
msgstr "1. Ignorance"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 6. Paṭhamaaññatarabhikkhusutta → bhikkhusuttaṃ (bj) | aññataro bhikkhu 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn45.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Paṭhamaaññatarabhikkhusutta"
msgstr "6. A Mendicant (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.6:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn45.6:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe … ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha … and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn45.6:1.3"
msgid "“‘brahmacariyaṃ, brahmacariyan’ti, bhante, vuccati."
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called the ‘spiritual path’."

msgctxt "sn45.6:1.4"
msgid ""
"Katamaṃ nu kho, bhante, brahmacariyaṃ, katamaṃ brahmacariyapariyosānan”ti?"
msgstr ""
"What is the spiritual path? And what is the culmination of the spiritual "
"path?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.8"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.6:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Ayameva kho, bhikkhu, ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo brahmacariyaṃ, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicant, the spiritual path is simply this noble eightfold path, that is:"

msgctxt "sn45.6:2.2"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""
"right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, "
"right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "sn45.6:2.3"
msgid "Yo kho, bhikkhu, rāgakkhayo dosakkhayo mohakkhayo—"
msgstr "The ending of greed, hate, and delusion."

msgctxt "sn45.6:2.4"
msgid "idaṃ brahmacariyapariyosānan”ti."
msgstr "This is the culmination of the spiritual path.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.6:2.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
